4h\u0323 Muslim 2987 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25818,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/28\/akhirah-allah-without-a-translator\/","url_meta":{"origin":1089,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Allah will speak to you without translator","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 28, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Adi ibn Hatim reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are none among you but that his Lord will speak to him in the Hereafter without a translator between them, nor a veil to separate them.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7005, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1016 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3791,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/24\/muslim-who-fasts-distant-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":1089,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: A Muslim who fasts will be distant from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever fasts a day in the way of Allah, Allah will move his face away from the Hellfire by a distance of seventy years.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2840, S\u